                            </p>
                            <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-audit-gold text-audit-navy px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold uppercase text-[10px] tracking-widest hover:bg-yellow-500 transition shadow-lg">
